This model is preferred over other vocabulary-based distributional models such as Word2Vec, Glove and others as it returns 4https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information security Fig.

The 5https://spacy.io/‚ÄòReal-time adaptive security‚Äô is converted to a feature vector that uses ‚Äòsecurity‚Äô as the word, ‚ÄòPROPN‚Äô as POS tag, ‚Äònsubj‚Äô as dependency tag and ‚Äò+‚Äô denotes the direction of the edge connecting it to the lowest common root node between the term pair.
